data.title: The Corporal and Others / A tizedes meg a tobbiek DVD
data.meta_description: Find A tizedes meg a tobbiek (The Corporal and Others) on DVD at Czechmovie.com. This 1965 Hungarian war comedy follows PFC Molnár, who, deciding WWII is over for him, stumbles upon an abandoned mansion and a group evading military duty. English subtitles available.
